import React from "react"
import ContentLoader from "react-content-loader"

const LandingPageLoader = (props) => (
  <ContentLoader 
    speed={2}
    width={1200}
    height={1400}
    viewBox="0 0 1200 1400"
    backgroundColor="#f3f3f3"
    foregroundColor="#ecebeb"
    {...props}
  >
    <rect x="9" y="15" rx="5" ry="5" width="1130" height="56" /> 
    <rect x="15" y="138" rx="0" ry="0" width="350" height="60" /> 
    <rect x="15" y="219" rx="0" ry="0" width="400" height="60" /> 
    <rect x="15" y="295" rx="5" ry="5" width="150" height="37" /> 
    <rect x="600" y="104" rx="5" ry="5" width="540" height="248" /> 
    <rect x="530" y="384" rx="0" ry="0" width="121" height="12" /> 
    <rect x="350" y="426" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="550" y="426" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="750" y="426" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="950" y="426" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="350" y="546" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="550" y="546" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="750" y="546" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="950" y="546" rx="5" ry="5" width="185" height="100" /> 
    <rect x="9" y="460" rx="5" ry="5" width="300" height="150" /> 
    <rect x="9" y="681" rx="0" ry="0" width="200" height="21" /> 
    <rect x="9" y="714" rx="0" ry="0" width="300" height="9" /> 
    <rect x="9" y="731" rx="0" ry="0" width="220" height="9" /> 
    <rect x="14" y="753" rx="5" ry="5" width="38" height="39" /> 
    <rect x="64" y="756" rx="0" ry="0" width="113" height="9" /> 
    <rect x="64" y="776" rx="0" ry="0" width="185" height="68" /> 
    <rect x="535" y="668" rx="5" ry="5" width="600" height="200" /> 
    <rect x="530" y="894" rx="0" ry="0" width="121" height="12" /> 
    <rect x="9" y="925" rx="10" ry="10" width="350" height="138" /> 
    <rect x="395" y="925" rx="10" ry="10" width="350" height="138" /> 
    <rect x="785" y="921" rx="10" ry="10" width="350" height="138" /> 
    <rect x="420" y="1127" rx="0" ry="0" width="300" height="14" /> 
    <rect x="475" y="1153" rx="0" ry="0" width="194" height="12" /> 
    <rect x="505" y="1181" rx="0" ry="0" width="136" height="8" /> 
    <rect x="470" y="1215" rx="5" ry="5" width="92" height="33" /> 
    <rect x="505" y="1194" rx="0" ry="0" width="136" height="8" /> 
    <rect x="590" y="1216" rx="5" ry="5" width="92" height="33" /> 
    <rect x="9" y="1281" rx="2" ry="2" width="1130" height="56" />
  </ContentLoader>
)

export default LandingPageLoader;
